reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Convenient for Getting to My Shoes
reviews.reviewText: At first I was dismayed when I opened the package because the plastic is so flimsy. I thought there is no way you can stack shoes with this. But, once you get the ends on and connect them, they are pretty sturdy. You can't stack a lot of weight on top but it will hold some stuff. I had all my shoes in clear boxes but getting to the bottom of the stack was a problem. I'd have to take everything down. Now, I just open the little door and grab my shoes. It really got my closet organized. I ordered the XLarge and it fits heels, tennis shoes, and some boots. Putting it together took some time to figure out. The ends appear not to fit but they do snap on if you get them just right. Once you get the hang of it, you can set them up pretty quickly. I will order another set, they work well for me.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Not bad for the price....patience on assembly required
reviews.reviewText: First, look at the price. The picture you see is fully assembled and of course it makes it look nicer than it actually is. You are not going to get 12 high end solid already assembled rigid plastic storage bins with easy open fronts. Also, these do not slide out.These are mass produced sheets of strong plastic that come completely flat made to expand into a shape of a box. So these are flexible and only rigid once the ends are assembled. Assembly is required and requires a bit of patience on the first one.In saying that, shoes should not require a strong storage box and these work fine unless you plan to use it every day all the time. I would recommend for storage & not for repeated use by many people. For shoes being used daily, I'd recommend something else or just use a regular shoe rack.Many styles of shoes will stand up straight in the box, but high heels may have to be turned sideways. I have also used for baseball caps as well.Assembly. It is very SIMPLE but patience is required! Expand the plastic sheets and make it form a box shape. Bend inward all tabs on both ends. Position the back onto one end and click in one side, then use your hands to guide the edges into the back, click in sides. Repeat for other end, paying attention to which way you want the little door to open. First few were slow, then it was easy from there on out.You have 12 to do so you might want to do a few of the same movements at the same time, or get someone to help.These will stack. You must push out the stacking tabs. The box on top has tabs on the bottom to slide into the top sides of box below to make it sturdy.Is this high end? No. Use care when opening the little door.Does it work well in the top of a closet? Yes. It took a lot of clutter and organized it very well, off the floor and into spaces we were not using.We bought another set for out closet so for what it is, we recommend it.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Neat and Tidy Shoe Organization Made Easy!
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the Large 12 Pack Shoe Storage Box, and I must say it's a game-changer for keeping my shoe collection organized and easily accessible. If you're looking for a practical solution to declutter your closet, these clear plastic stackable shoe organizers are a must-have.The large size of the storage boxes accommodates various shoe types and sizes, making it a versatile solution for my entire shoe collection. The clear plastic design allows me to see the contents of each box without having to open it, saving time when deciding on the perfect pair for the day.Stackability is a fantastic feature, maximizing vertical space in my closet and providing a clean and uniform look. The boxes interlock securely, preventing any accidental spills or tipping. This has been especially helpful in creating a neat and tidy closet space.The durability of the plastic is impressive – sturdy enough to withstand the weight of multiple shoe pairs while remaining transparent for easy visibility. The ventilation holes also ensure that my shoes stay fresh and well-ventilated, preventing any unwanted odors.Assembly is a breeze – no tools required. The boxes snap together effortlessly, and the overall construction feels robust and reliable. I appreciate the ease with which I can access my shoes while keeping them protected from dust and damage.In conclusion, the Large 12 Pack Shoe Storage Box is a fantastic investment for anyone looking to declutter their closet and maintain an organized shoe collection. These stackable organizers are practical, durable, and a visually appealing solution to elevate your closet organization game. Highly recommended!
